data.description: Welcome to this charming end-of-row townhouse nestled in the heart of Woodbridge, VA! This spacious 3-level home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering ample space for comfortable living. Enjoy the convenience of all wood floors throughout and a beautifully renovated kitchen, perfect for entertaining guests or preparing family meals. Step outside to relax and unwind on the inviting deck in the backyard, a tranquil retreat after a long day.   Located just 15 minutes away from the bustling Potomac Mills Mall and close to Stonebridge Plaza, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. With 2 designated parking spots and plenty of visitor parking available, convenience is at your fingertips.  This property is ideal for buyers seeking a motivated seller, with a sell-to-buy contingency in place. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful townhouse your new home sweet home!
